                    <article itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/NewsArticle" itemid="http://www.theblaze.com/stories/2015/02/08/what-would-really-happen-if-homeland-security-department-was-shut-down-turns-out-conservatives-are-right-about-it/">
         
